Blocks.childText: 1893 Life A. M2128 FGX5 (s) PREFACE. B ELIEVING Song to be one of God's appointed ways of spreading the gospel, we send this little messenger forth in His name. "I am the light of the world : he that followeth me shall not walk in darkness, but shall have the Light of Life."-JOHN VII: 12. EDW. S. FOGG. T. W. BARKER. EMORY UNIVERSITY THEOLOGY LIBRARY
